sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant PDA as 👥 PDA (mobile)
    participant API as 🛎️ Front Desk (route handler)
    participant DB as 🗄️ Database
    participant LOG as 📓 Audit log
    participant BELL as 🚶 Bellhop (waitUntil)
    participant RT as 📡 Realtime
    participant PT as 👤 Patient (web, online)

    PDA->>API: New record for patient 42
    API->>DB: save the record
    API->>LOG: write audit entry
    API-->>PDA: 200 done
    API->>BELL: hand off via waitUntil

    Note over BELL: Runs after the response goes out. Best-effort, no retries.

    BELL->>RT: is patient 42 online?
    RT-->>BELL: yes, viewing records on web
    BELL->>RT: publish to patient:42 (ID only, no PHI)
    RT-->>PT: 🔔 live event arrives
    PT->>PT: row appears in records table, no refresh
    Note over BELL: Online → in-app only. Offline → push and email. Vendor blip = dropped.
